name: TOACLUB
description: Welcome to the TOA Club from Josh Thorsen, founder of Teens On Acid. 99 hand-drawn 1/1 trading cards that serve perfectly as your new pfp. Collect as many as you want or choose just one that best represents you. With 5 rarities available, there's a Teens on Acid character for all of us. At the full sale of the set, all holders will get exclusive access to a prism version of their card. Real world prints rewards are also in consideration.
